OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRail strike: Law change    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwould allow agency staff to
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcover industrial action    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has announced plans to  
OL,6, change the law to enable employers to  
OL,7, use agency staff to cover staffing gaps
OL,8, during strikes.                        
OL,10,FMinisters say the measure, which needs 
OL,11,FParliament's approval, would limit the 
OL,12,Fimpact of future strikes.              
OL,14,FBut opposition parties and unions have 
OL,15,Fcriticised the plan, arguing it would  
OL,16,Fundermine pay and working conditions.  
OL,18,FIt comes as rail strikes in Britain    
OL,19,Fresumed after talks between unions and 
OL,20,Frail bosses broke down on Wednesday.   
